monitoringPlanCommentData.monitoringPlanComment: Replaced and installed like kind CO2 and NOx analyzers on both the Common Stack and Unit 3.   The new NOx analyzers are dual range.   Replaced and installed like kind SO2 analyzer on the Common Stack.   Installed new probe at Unit 3 duct.   Installed in umbilical.
Corrected dates the new analyzers were placed in service from 9/2 to 9/1 on Unit 3  and corrected the end and start dates on the common stack.
